title: Cressida Dick is first woman to head macho Scotland Yard
text: show ad Another male bastion falls: Just 5ft tall, she's the bluestocking who pounded the beat, was implicated in the killing of an innocent man after 7/7 and helped jail Stephen Lawrence's killers. Now Cressida Dick is the first woman to head a very macho Scotland Yard Cressida Dick has broken through the glass ceiling to become the Met Police top officer She will become arguably the most senior police officer in the world Ms Dick spent the last two years in a senior role at the Foreign and Commonwealth Office The family of Jean Charles de Menezes had called for her appointment to be blocked
